"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/457767","Department of Health","false","2016-03-09","<p>In January, the Secretary of State for Education and Secretary of State for Health announced the Government’s intention to establish a new regulatory body for social work to drive up standards with an ambition to raise the quality of social work, education, training and practice in both children’s and adult’s social work.</p><p> </p><p>As part of this work, we are exploring the feasibility of establishing a national register for Approved Mental Health Professionals.</p>","North East Bedfordshire","Alistair Burt",,"2016-03-09T11:14:27.623Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/457767/answer","Biography information for Alistair Burt","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/457767/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/457767/answer",,,,,"17","Health","Health","2016-03-04","Mental Health Services","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Health, pursuant to the Answer of 3 March 2016 to Question 28900, on mental health services, if he will make it his policy to collect that information.","false","Biography information for Luciana Berger","Liverpool, Wavertree","Luciana Berger","29825"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/457768","Department of Health","false","2016-03-09","<p>There are no plans at present to collect this information but this will be kept under review in light of work being undertaken this year by Health Education England.</p>","Ipswich","Ben Gummer",,"2016-03-09T17:13:36.307Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/457768/answer","Biography information for Ben Gummer","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/457768/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/457768/answer",,,,,"17","Health","Health","2016-03-04","Nurses: Training","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Health, pursuant to the Answer of 3 March 2016 to Question 28901, on nurses: training, if he will make it his policy to collect that information.","false","Biography information for Luciana Berger","Liverpool, Wavertree","Luciana Berger","29826"
