"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/457437","Cabinet Office","false","2016-03-09","<p>The total expenditure of the Commission will be published in due course.</p>","West Suffolk","Matthew Hancock","29652","2016-03-09T09:19:20.07Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/457437/answer","Biography information for Matt Hancock","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/457437/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/457437/answer",,,,,"53","Cabinet Office","Cabinet Office","2016-03-03","Commission on Freedom of Information: Allowances","1","House of Commons","To ask the Minister for the Cabinet Office, what expenses were claimed by members of the Independent Commission on Freedom of Information.","false","Biography information for Tom Watson","West Bromwich East","Tom Watson","29653"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/457438","Cabinet Office","false","2016-03-10","<p>The Commission was supported by a small secretariat which comprised of one full time secondee from the Cabinet Office and two secondees from the Ministry of Justice, all of whom are below the Senior Civil Service. In addition, adhoc administrative support was provided on request.</p>","West Suffolk","Matthew Hancock",,"2016-03-10T14:08:00.807Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/457438/answer","Biography information for Matt Hancock","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/457438/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/457438/answer",,,,,"53","Cabinet Office","Cabinet Office","2016-03-03","Commission on Freedom of Information: Staff","1","House of Commons","To ask the Minister for the Cabinet Office, how many officials of his Department provided support to the Independent Commission on Freedom of Information.","false","Biography information for Tom Watson","West Bromwich East","Tom Watson","29654"
